main event: A UFO observation was reported in Glassboro, New Jersey on February 25, 1967.
interesting points: The observation was recorded in Project Blue Book,The report concluded there was insufficient data for evaluation,There was no physical evidence presented,The report included a questionnaire for the observer to fill out,The observer reported seeing a bearing light for about 15-20 minutes from inside their home.
sighted object: a bearing light in the sky
witness description: personal account from an individual who filled out the report
